                    <p class="center">Unit of Measurement: Ampere (A)</p>
                    <p class="center">1 A = 1 C/s</p>
                    <p class="center fragment"><i>How many charged particles pass through per second?</i></p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>Fundamental Electrical Quantities: <span class="green">Voltage</span></h2>
                
                    <p class="center">Energy required to push charges</p>
                
                    <p class="center">Unit of Measurement: Volt (V)</p>
                    <p class="center">1 V = 1 J/C</p>
                    <p class="center fragment"><i>How much energy is spent to push an electron?</i></p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>Fundamental Electrical Quantities: <span class="green">Resistance</span></h2>
