				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>Fundamental Electrical Quantities: <span class="green">Power</span></h2>   
                
                    <p class="center">Rate at which energy is expended</p>
                
                    <p class="center">Unit of Measurement: Watt (W)</p>
                    <p class="center">1 W = 1 VA = 1 (J/C)(C/s) = 1 J/s</p>
